FBIS3-22980 "jptot008__l94081" JPRS-TOT-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 1 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA INDIA Suspected `Militants' Kill Tea Company Manager in Assam BK1502134394 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1230 GMT 15 Feb 94 BK1502134394 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] In Assam, suspected ULFA [United Liberation Front of Assam] militants shot dead the general manager of a tea company early this morning at (Talab) Tea Estate of Tinsukhia District in upper Assam. Police sources at Guwahati said the miscreants stole his vehicle, which was recovered later from a nearby village. A vigorous manhunt is on to nab the culprits.
